        <item>
            <title>【評測】MacBook Pro M4 2024  詳細效能評測 + 選購指南分析 7 大要點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/macbook-pro-m4-2024-review/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=macbook-pro-m4-2024-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/macbook-pro-m4-2024-review/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:00:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[macbook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[macbook pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Pro 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Pro M4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電腦]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274013</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 最新推出 M4 MacBook Pro 系列，再度在設計、效能以及智能功能上推陳出新。這次升級進一步提升硬件效能，令處理影片剪輯等多媒體創作者注入新動力之外，還於機身設計上進行微調，並引入 Apple Intelligence 的 AI 智能功能，大幅提高用户工作效率。M4 版 MacBook Pro 展現出高效能、電池耐用、配套豐富、使用便利等，大家對高效筆電的極致追求。以下小編會就 MacBook Pro 軟硬件各方面進行評測，看看你在選購時，選擇貼合自己需要的型號、選配選項。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274095 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>選購要點 <b>1. </b>設計細節</h2><p>新款 MacBook Pro 的外型在上代基礎上進行了微調，利用特別電鍍技術製作「太空黑」配色，給人低調而奢華的機身設計。MagSafe 充電線與太空黑機身也有特別搭配，相比起 MacBook Air 的午夜黑，更加增強了黑色視覺效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>MacBook Pro 太空黑在充電線上也改良到更加「黑」，顏色上配套做得更好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左手邊是午夜黑的充電線，右手邊是 MacBook Pro 太空黑所附屬的充電線</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左方是今次介紹的太空黑 MacBook Pro M4 版本，右手邊的是午夜黑 MacBook Air。可見兩者色系有分別</p><h2>選購要點 <b>2. 1000nits </b>高亮度熒幕與 <b>Nano Texture </b>抗反光納米紋理顯示器</h2><p>新款 MacBook Pro 用家可選擇加錢配置具抗反光功能的 Nano Texture 納米紋理顯示器，提升在複雜燈光環境，或者強光環境下的顯示效果。例如在咖啡室，室內可能有好多零散燈光，一個個燈泡顯示在你的畫面上，你甚至可在畫面看到自己的樣貌。Nano Texture 納米紋理顯示器就可大幅減低這些反射現象。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274096 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274044 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-694x283.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="283" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-694x283.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>但你也要留意，就同手機的抗反射芒貼一樣，即使 Apple 已做得很好，但仍然有光亮度低減、對比度與黑位深度有輕微下跌的現象，不一定適合對畫面效果有極度要求，例如圖像處理的用家。建議使用者根據需求選擇。之不過這部 M4 MacBook Pro 帶來了全新 Liquid Retina XDR 顯示器，觀看一般內容時可提供達 1000nits 光亮度，而在顯示 HDR 內容時光亮度更可達 1600nits，它可以抵銷到 Nano Texture 納米紋理顯示器對光線透通度的影響，除非你經常需要把熒幕亮度開到最大，否則光度低減的問題可以忽視。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
